# TypeScript & Code Quality Guidelines

## TypeScript Configuration

### Strict Mode
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) enables strict TypeScript settings
- `strict: true` - Enables all strict type checking options
- `noEmit: true` - Type checking only, no JavaScript output
- `skipLibCheck: true` - Skip type checking of declaration files

### Path Mapping
- Use `@/*` alias for `src/*` imports
- Import components: `import { Component } from "@/components/component"`
- Import utilities: `import { cn } from "@/lib/utils"`
- Import data: `import { DATA } from "@/data/resume"`

